Anglo Irish Bank Dodges Hedge Funds' Suit
A New York federal judge on Monday tossed a suit filed by two hedge funds against Anglo Irish Bank Corp. Ltd., ruling that the bank, now owned by the Irish government, is protected by sovereign immunity.


